[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m557[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m558[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m559[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m560[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe evaluation report clearly identifies the issue: the last patch attempt removed [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `JAVA_OBJDATA` enum value but failed to remove the `[0m[1;35mstartJavaObjData[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat references it at line [0m[1;36m102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m105[0m[39m of `RTFEmbObjHandler.java`. This incomplete [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremoval caused the compilation error.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Core Issue[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe vulnerability is a Remote Code Execution [0m[1;39m([0m[39mRCE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m vulnerability arising from [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munrestricted deserialization of Java objects embedded in RTF documents via [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mObjectInputStream.readObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. The attack vector is the `javaobjdata` RTF [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontrol destination, which is a Tika-specific extension [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot part of the standard [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRTF specification[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause Location[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mRTFEmbObjHandler.handleCompletedObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at lines [0m[1;36m213[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m224[0m[39m performs unsafe [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeserialization[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The deserialization is triggered through the `javaobjdata` control word [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing chain[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Multiple components work together: `TextExtractor`, `GroupState`, and [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`RTFEmbObjHandler`[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Previous Patch Analysis[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe last patch attempt correctly identified all the locations but missed removing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `[0m[1;35mstartJavaObjData[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m105[0m[39m in RTFEmbObjHandler.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, causing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe compilation error. The patch must be reapplied with this additional removal.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. RTFEmbObjHandler.java Changes[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Remove all javaobjdata-related code:**[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Line [0m[1;36m21[0m[39m**: Remove the import statement[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove: `import java.io.ObjectInputStream;`[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rationale: This import is only used for the vulnerable deserialization code[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m105[0m[39m**: Remove the entire `[0m[1;35mstartJavaObjData[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This is the missing piece from the previous patch[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This method sets `state = EMB_STATE.JAVA_OBJDATA` which causes the compilation[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m213[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m224[0m[39m**: Remove the vulnerable deserialization code block[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the entire `else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstate == EMB_STATE.JAVA_OBJDATA[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This eliminates the RCE vulnerability by removing [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mObjectInputStream.readObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39md[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Line [0m[1;36m283[0m[39m**: Remove the `JAVA_OBJDATA` enum value[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove: `JAVA_OBJDATA, [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mrecording[0m[39m java obj data`[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The enum will have three values: PICT, OBJDATA, NADA[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. GroupState.java Changes[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Remove the javaobjdata field:**[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m38[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m39[0m[39m**: Remove field declaration[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the comment and field: `[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95min[0m[39m javaobjdata` and `public boolean [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjavaobjdata;`[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Line [0m[1;36m67[0m[39m**: Remove field copy in constructor[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove: `javaobjdata = other.javaobjdata;`[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. TextExtractor.java Changes[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Remove all javaobjdata processing logic:**[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m1274[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1276[0m[39m**: Remove the control destination handler[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the entire `else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mequals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"javaobjdata"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This prevents the parser from recognizing the javaobjdata control word[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Line [0m[1;36m487[0m[39m**: Modify the condition to remove javaobjdata check[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Change from: `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgroupState.objdata == true || groupState.javaobjdata [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== true || groupState.pictDepth == [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m`[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Change to: `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgroupState.objdata == true || groupState.pictDepth == [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m`[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m1473[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1479[0m[39m**: Remove the [0m[1;35mprocessGroupEnd[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m handling for javaobjdata[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the entire `else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgroupState.javaobjdata == true[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` block[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This prevents completion processing of javaobjdata[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Test Code Changes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mRTFParserTest.java[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Remove tests for the removed functionality:**[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Line [0m[1;36m27[0m[39m**: Remove import [0m[1;39m([0m[39monly if not used elsewhere[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `import java.io.ObjectOutputStream;`[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Line [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m**: Remove import [0m[1;39m([0m[39monly if not used elsewhere[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `import org.apache.commons.codec.binary.Hex;`[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m516[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m528[0m[39m**: Remove the `[0m[1;35mtestJavaObj[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` test method entirely[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This test validates the removed functionality[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39md[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m530[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m536[0m[39m**: Remove `[0m[1;35mwriteObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` helper method[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only used by testJavaObj[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39me[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m538[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m548[0m[39m**: Remove `[0m[1;35mwrap[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` helper method[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only used by testJavaObj[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mf[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m **Lines [0m[1;36m550[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m558[0m[39m**: Remove `[0m[1;35mserialize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` helper method[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only used by testJavaObj[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Test Resource File Removal[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Remove the test template file:**[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Delete: [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-parsers/tika-parsers-standard/tika-parsers-standard-modules/tika-parser-micro[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msoft-module/src/test/resources/test-documents/rtf/rtfJavaObjTemplate.rtf`[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This file is only used by the removed testJavaObj test[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This is the Optimal Approach[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Complete Removal**: Unlike the previous attempt, this removes ALL references [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto javaobjdata, including the missed `[0m[1;35mstartJavaObjData[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, ensuring [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation success.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Security**: Completely eliminates the RCE vulnerability by removing the unsafe[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeserialization code path. There's no safe way to deserialize untrusted Java [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobjects from external files.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Preserves Existing Functionality**: The patch only removes javaobjdata support[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile preserving:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Standard RTF objdata handling [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOLE embedded objects[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - RTF picture [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpict[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m handling[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All other RTF parsing functionality[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Minimal Impact**: The javaobjdata feature is a Tika-specific extension, not [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpart of the RTF specification, so removing it doesn't break standard RTF support.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Preserves Existing Logic[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **OBJDATA handling remains intact**: The legitimate RTFObjDataParser continues to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparse standard OLE embedded objects safely using structured parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeserialization[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **PICT handling remains intact**: Picture extraction continues to work normally[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Metadata extraction preserved**: RTFMetadata.EMB_CLASS is still used by objdata[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandling to store OLE class names[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **State machine preserved**: The EMB_STATE enum still functions with three valid [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstates [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPICT, OBJDATA, NADA[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Issues[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Fixes Compilation Error**: Removes the `[0m[1;35mstartJavaObjData[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method that [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreferences the removed `JAVA_OBJDATA` enum value[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Eliminates RCE Vulnerability**: Removes all deserialization code paths that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcan be triggered by external RTF files[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Removes Attack Surface**: RTF files containing `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m\*\javaobjdata [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` will now[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe safely ignored [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe `\*` prefix means unknown destinations should be ignored per[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRTF spec[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Breaking Change**: RTF files with embedded Java objects will no longer have [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthose objects extracted[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: This is intentional for security. Such files are extremely rare [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand the feature was a security risk.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Test Removal**: The testJavaObj test will be removed[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: This is necessary as the feature is being removed. The test [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidates vulnerable functionality.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Import Cleanup**: ObjectOutputStream and Hex imports removed from test file[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Only remove if not used by other tests. Need to verify no other [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests use these imports.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Similar Solutions in Codebase[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
